Package com.github.tommyettinger.ds.interop

package com.github.tommyettinger.ds.interop
Includes code to save jdkgdxds, digital, and juniper types to libGDX JSON, as well as to convert between jdkgdxds types and their libGDX counterparts.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    ConversionToGDX
    Converts from arbitrary data structures that implement JDK interfaces to libGDX data structures (which typically implement Iterable at most).
    ConversionToJDK
    Converts libGDX data structures to the JDK-interface-compatible data structures in jdkgdxds.
    JsonSupport
